<p>The Code<span style="color: red; font-weight: bold;">RED</span> emergency notification system is used to alert Taliaferro County residents and businesses in the event of an emergency. A notification can be for an evacuation, missing child or a weather related emergency for example. Residents and businesses in Taliaferro County are encouraged to sign up for CodeRED to ensure they receive timely emergency notifications along with important information and instructions when alerts are issued.</p>
<p>Alerts can be sent to a cell phone, land line, text and or email. With CodeRED, the subscriber also has the option to receive Severe Weather Warnings with the Emergency Notifications. Early warning notification could prove to be instrumental in preparedness and lifesaving. CodeRED enrollment is free to Taliaferro County residents and businesses. <strong>To enroll, click on the logo and complete the enrollment page.</strong> Please tell friends and family members about this free invaluable service.</p>
